    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/cd8e362b331a8af266926c74c1605e7d.poster.avif?t=1730163603\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/cd8e362b331a8af266926c74c1605e7d.webm?t=1730163603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/cd8e362b331a8af266926c74c1605e7d.mp4?t=1730163603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多选项、单结局的视觉小说，游戏时长大约10小时</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >华丽的视觉效果、CG美术和动画风格的角色立绘</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众星云集的声优阵容</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※部分功能和设置与Android版本相同，因此不包括PC原版的特殊日历剧情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/59675ad8c0a487a4f521b38714dafff5.avif?t=1730163603\" width=616 height=2148 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事大纲</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平凡的高中生高杉星司在公园里结识了名为玛亚的少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然玛亚言行诡异，但她那种看似迷糊却又充满魅力的性格让星司深受吸引。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天，一位异形魔神忽然出现在了两人面前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原来，玛亚其实是与魔神签订了契约的魔法少女，她能驱使暗黑之力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >星司阴差阳错地成为了玛亚的使魔，并与魔神签订契约，协助它对抗敌对魔神。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为使魔后，星司拥有了使用魔法的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但作为代价，他的脚踝上多出了一根魔法绳，这根绳子将他与玛亚连在了一起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了维持生命，星司必须始终待在玛亚身边，不断地从她那里汲取魔力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是，两人开始了同居生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于玛亚缺乏常识，在自己的使魔面前毫无戒备心，所以他们的生活中充满了令人脸红心跳的意外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >星司和玛亚的同居生活究竟会走向何方？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >登场角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/2ea455d133d91277da586e8c1848e0d6.avif?t=1730163603\" width=616 height=230 /></span><strong>玛亚‧克利燕科</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音：桃山いおん</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被魔神选中，并与之签订契约的少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她比主人公星司年长一岁，会使用暗黑魔法，且剑术十分高超。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格单纯而死板，深受老家同伴们的敬爱和信赖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，她也有迷糊的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机缘巧合之下，她结识了星司，两人在暑假期间开始了同居生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宿星的女朋友2的女主角。（在1和3中无法攻略）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你既是我的使魔，也是我的战友，希望我们能够互相扶持。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/ff4e8a3a622636d2600b2fd08f407f25.avif?t=1730163603\" width=616 height=230 /></span><strong>佐竹 鹿子</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音：猫村ゆき</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被冠以危宿一之名的群星。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管她只是一名高一学生，但猎杀恶魔的技巧却出奇地高超。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格淡漠，不喜欢与他人打交道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擅长一切家务活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她打从心底尊敬既是师傅又是学姐的夕里，总是心甘情愿地照顾她的生活起居。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宿星的女朋友3的女主角。（在1和2中无法攻略）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“与恶魔有瓜葛的人都该被消灭。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/9d1af77af4b25c2fcce6402922e94609.avif?t=1730163603\" width=616 height=230 /></span><strong>上泉 夕里</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音：桃井いちご</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被冠以参宿七之名的群星。同时也被评鉴为最高等级的一等星。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为光系魔法的专家，她总能以压倒性的火力将恶魔烧成灰烬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外表也相当出众，在学校时会装成乖乖女，所以在男学生中拥有极高的人气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她性格开朗，看似轻浮，实际上自尊心很强，处处想胜人一筹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与刚强的外在面貌相反，她的身心其实都很脆弱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宿星的女朋友1的女主角。（在2和3中无法攻略）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“我会用我那傲人的光辉解决一切问题！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/30e590d31b293ba32f16bf77db83f2f8.avif?t=1730163603\" width=616 height=230 /></span><strong>佩特拉·格林恩</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音：小鳥居夕花</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玛亚的同乡晚辈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她与玛亚关系亲密，并对她怀有深厚的敬意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >熟人都说她“像一条吵吵闹闹的小狗”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格大胆奔放，对谁都充满了热情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她十分健谈，由于在童年时期经历过许多苦难，所以拥有一颗强大的内心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比主人公星司小一岁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她似乎是为了追随玛亚才来到日本的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“大姐头！大姐头大姐头！好久不见了，我是佩特拉！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361740/extras/5ee708e02f614f347eef8a2f69ef6a4d.avif?t=1730163603\" width=616 height=230 /></span><strong>与那岭 芙慈子</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音：新田優羽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前任群星，曾被冠以泣二之名。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现如今，她成为了闪亮星空会东神奈川支部的内勤人员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在她还是群星的时候，她所使用的治愈魔法就广受好评。尽管已经引退，但她仍是现任群星们的可靠后盾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她至今仍擅长施展高等治愈魔法，且性格既温柔又和善，深受大家的喜欢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“我想用自己发明的魔法道具来帮助大家～”</p>",
